## tooling for generating xbrl taxonomies

### generate a base taxonomy with calculation links
input: list of concept names and summation links

output: 
	1) xsd file declaring concepts, similar to http://dev-node.uksouth.cloudapp.azure.com:7788/static/taxonomy/basic.xsd
	2) xml file declaring calculation links, like http://dev-node.uksouth.cloudapp.azure.com:7788/static/taxonomy/basic-calculation.xml
	
our sw has various special-purpose modules. One is for parsing bank account statements and inferring appropriate 
